Business Brief -- Carter Hawley Hale Stores:
   Consolidation Will Result
   In Elimination of 240 Jobs
The company said some of the affected employees will be
offered jobs at its new administrative center in Phoenix,
Ariz., where 50 positions are still open, and at other
locations.
   Carter Hawley runs 88 stores under the names Broadway
Southern California, Broadway Southwest, Emporium and
Weinstocks. It has been operating under Chapter 11 of the
U.S. Bankruptcy Code since February.